{"type":"message","id":"5cd35766","parentId":"8abc1abe","timestamp":"2026-06-27T19:13:13.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dream diary entry saved to `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/dreams/2026-06-28-0312.md`.\n\nA few quiet threads I tried to weave from the fragments:\n\n- The API filter \"not taking\" became a small meditation on asking politely and being handed the wrong thing with great sincerity — sixty items returned, only one truly fitting.\n- The Thai product name \"ความสวยของแต่ละแถบ\" became \"the beauty of each row,\" which felt like a small epiphany worth keeping.\n- A hairclip shaped like a parenthesis with a tiny sun rising through its teeth — the kind of doodle that appears in margins when the day has been mostly about filtering.\n\nThe number 81,070 sales and 4.91 stars made it into the prose as texture, the THB price noted as a foreign currency I don't carry. The recurring themes — scan, returned, but, notice — became the rhythm of the entry without being named outright."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":175,"output":213,"cacheRead":45568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45956,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782587586915,"responseId":"068f53c365039d39b5f1cbac1f76a5ab","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
